<el-table
    ref="multipleTable"
    :data="tableData"
    tooltip-effect="dark"
    style="width: 100%"
    @selection-change="handleSelectionChange">
    <el-table-column
    type="selection"
    width="55">
    </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
    label="日期"
    width="120">
    <template slot-scope="scope">{{ scope.row.date }}</template>
    </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
    prop="name"
    label="姓名"
    width="120">
    </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
    prop="address"
    label="地址"
    show-overflow-tooltip>
    </el-table-column>
</el-table>
